flowchart TD
  SOP[SOP text] --> Atomize[Stage 1: SOP atomization]
  Atomize --> Ops[01-ops.json]
  Ops --> Hypergraph[Stage 2: knowledge hypergraph construction]
  Hypergraph --> Nodes[02-nodes.json]
  Hypergraph --> Edges[03-hyperedges.json]
  Nodes --> Requirements[Stage 3: deterministic R1-R10 mapping]
  Edges --> Requirements
  Requirements --> ReqTable[04-requirements.json]
  ReqTable --> Infer{LLM configured?}
  Infer -- no --> Clarify[Record LLM fallback clarification]
  Infer -- yes --> Candidates[Generate and deduplicate candidate requirements]
  Candidates --> ReqTable
  Clarify --> Review[Stage 5: review and coverage]
  ReqTable --> Review
  Review --> Coverage[05-coverage.json]
  Review --> Report[report.md and diagrams]
  Review --> Meta[run-meta.json]

